title: LF Plat+ Jungle to join CTD Esports for various tournaments + OOL
body:
Looking for a Platinum + Jungle main to join our team, preferrable with 5's experiance. 

We're playing in the upcoming split of SumSoc and looking to join the OOL.

This is for a starting roster position so please provide your OP.GG link and dont be a one trick :)

Thanks!
